Project Overview
Food Express is a static food ordering web application built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript and deployed on Amazon Web Services (AWS) using Amazon S3 Static Website Hosting.
The project allows users to view a food menu, add items to an order, and place an order through a simple front‑end interface.
This project demonstrates hands‑on experience with AWS core services, static web hosting, and cloud security best practices.


Technologies Used

Frontend: HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript
Cloud Platform: Amazon Web Services (AWS)
AWS Services:

Amazon S3 (Static Website Hosting)
AWS IAM & S3 Bucket Policy


