✨ Features

Display food menu with prices
Add items to order dynamically
Calculate total order value in real time
Collect customer name and phone number
Display order confirmation message
Responsive and user‑friendly UI
Hosted securely on AWS S3


Deployment Steps

Created an S3 bucket with a globally unique name
Disabled Block Public Access for static content
Uploaded website files (index.html, style.css, script.js)
Enabled Static Website Hosting on S3
Created and attached an S3 Bucket Policy to allow public read access (s3:GetObject)
Tested the website using the S3 website endpoint URL

Security Configuration

Access controlled using S3 Bucket Policy
Only GetObject permission allowed
No write or delete permissions exposed
Public access limited to website content only
